---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Studio — Erik Knuppel" description="Art, gaming sessions, and creative work.">
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight">
        Studio
      </h1>
      <a href="/api/logout" class="text-sm text-earth hover:text-ink transition-colors">Log out</a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-ink-light leading-relaxed mb-12">
      Art, gaming sessions, and creative work. This is the private corner.
    </p>

    <div class="border-t border-cream-dark pt-8 mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Gaming Sessions</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-4">Tales of the Radiant Citadel — D&D 5E campaign, 109 sessions deep.</p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/studio/session-109" class="block p-5 bg-cream-dark rounded-xl hover:bg-gold/20 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-warm transition-colors">Session 109</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-earth">March 3, 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Picking up from session 108's cliffhanger, the party engaged Nakhorus and his army of 400+ ghouls on the underside of th</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/studio/session-108" class="block p-5 bg-cream-dark rounded-xl hover:bg-gold/20 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-warm transition-colors">Session 108</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-earth">Feb 24, 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Sewers, skeletons, sludge, and a ghoul army. The party chases Nak Horizon to the underside of the Citadel.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-cream-dark pt-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Art</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Coming soon.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
